          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyJoV-cnHWBcN8GpnkEb-AVc4k1-bNV9kf8g8EoX5I99J0ai7ElQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I came in expecting the usual medical experience: confusing forms, mysterious wait times, and at least one person sighing at a computer. Instead, I was unsettlingly well cared for.\n\nThe staff were too competent. Appointments ran on time. Questions were answered clearly. Tests were explained before I had the chance to Google worst-case scenarios. At one point, I became suspicious since this place was operating with the efficiency of a well-rehearsed heist crew, except the goal was my health.\n\nDoctors listened, staff were kind, and nobody made me feel like an inconvenience for existing. I left with a clear plan, fewer worries, and the odd feeling that adults were fully in charge.\n\nFrankly, if you enjoy chaos and uncertainty, this is not the medical center for you. But if you want professionalism, intelligence, and care delivered with calm confidence, this place is annoyingly excellent. Would absolutely trust them with my health again, but reluctantly, because now my standards are ruined.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGS1EyaE5abmxzTWpZeWVWaDVZMnBGY25abFFuYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xb2cd13949eaff9e3!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlFKQ2hNZnlsMjYyeVh5Y2pFcnZlQnc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "5 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-01-20T00:40:37+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Kat",
